Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time it takes to reach SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation after SW-Reviewer Agreed is performed
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average duration of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants that include SW-Reviewer Agreed followed by SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed occurs

Name: Time elapsed from the last occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed to the start of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants that proceed to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Minimum waiting time to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation after all assigned reviewers have agreed (i.e., after the final SW-Reviewer Agreed event per case)
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average time from SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in cases where SW-Reviewer Agreed occurred
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Time of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation compared to the time of SW-Reviewer Agreed within the same variant path
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in the longest-performing variant containing both activities
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Cycle time of SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in cases that experienced reviewer delays (e.g., SW-Reviewer No Response or SW-Reviewer Declined prior to SW-Reviewer Agreed)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation' and the end of case where activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response occurs

Name: Average time it takes SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation to be completed after the first SW-Reviewer Agreed in multi-reviewer assignments
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time from SW-Reviewer Agreed to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants that resulted in SW-EIC Major Revision versus SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time between the final SW-Reviewer Agreed and SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation across all successful review paths
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'
